        <Parent_String>flat-bottomed watercraft [300232673], monohulls [300232670], watercraft by sectional form [300232669], watercraft by form [300232663], watercraft by specific type [300219289], watercraft [300042940], vehicles (transportation) [300219258], Transportation Vehicles (hierarchy name) [300042929], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
